r the chief executive of the city in opposition to the present mayor D C Thomas of live wire fame who has declared him self a candidate for reelection Both candidates are being strongly backed by their supporters and friends and their fight will be one to the finish Alder man Lester has declared himself in no uncertain terms as to the law enforce ment and city government and in this ho will have the support of the citizens who desire better conditions M Les ter has served the city long and well as an alderman having served some eight years in that capacity and has always worked for the best interests of its citi zens He has done excellent work on the committee appointed to investigate the water franchise and to a greut ex tent is responsible for many of the con cessions made by the water company Mr Lesters principal appeal to the citi zens is his past record of service PETITION OUT"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2023-06-25T23:49:53.098Z", "group": ["ndnp/sdhi", "south-dakota-state-historical-society-state-archives-awardee"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/resource/sn2001063549/1908-03-06/ed-1/?sp=9", "image_url": ["https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:sdhi:batch_sdhi_lightning_ver01:data:sn2001063549:00415625017:1908030601:0034/full/pct:6.25/0/default.jpg#h=404&w=284", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:sdhi:batch_sdhi_lightning_ver01:data:sn2001063549:00415625017:1908030601:0034/full/pct:12.5/0/default.jpg#h=808&w=569", "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service?segment=/service/ndnp/sdhi/batch_sdhi_lightning_ver01/data/sn2001063549/00415625017/1908030601/0034.xml&format=alto_xml"], "index": 9, "language": ["english"], "location": ["south dakota", "codington county", "watertown", "united states", "codington"], "location_city": ["watertown"], "location_country": ["united states"], "location_county": ["codington"], "location_state": ["south dakota"], "mime_type": ["image/jp2", "appli